          "originalWidth": 400,
          "originalHeight": 213,
          "caption": "Honeywell and the MIT Center for Sustainability Science and Strategy released research showing AI-enabled technologies could reduce global production costs for traditional oil-based fuels by up to $55 billion annually within five years of application and $225 billion by 2050. For LNG, AI-based technologies could cut annual costs by $15 billion within five years and up to $80 billion by 2050.",
